remarks:
The membership relation is irreflexive: no set is a member of itself. Theorem 105 of [Suppes] p. 54.  (This is trivial to prove from ~ zfregfr and ~ efrirr , but this proof is direct from the Axiom of Regularity.) (Contributed by NM, 19-Aug-1993.)
